description:
This is a 27 minute workout called 'Guided Meditation for Deep Relaxation | Gurudev' from the channel Meditations By Gurudev.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Deep Recharge and The Sleep Prep vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Meditations By Gurudev is the Art Of Living's official YouTube channel for all meditations by Gurudev Sri Sri Ravi Shankar. 

Gurudev has made meditation simple, easy and accessible to all! He has improved the emotional, mental and physical health of millions across the globe through his meditations

If you're looking for a stress free, anxiety free, worry free life, then this channel is for you! All you need to do is sit back, relax and follow Gurudev's instructions!

Are you interested to learn meditation? Let us know by sharing your details on the link below, we will get back to you with details : https://aoliv.in/interested-meditation
